</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>外媒揭中國地下挖 Bitcoin 風潮仍盛，各地礦工不摘手段冒險開採</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/bitcoin-4/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bitcoin-4</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 06:41:39 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[以太幣]]></category><category><![CDATA[加密貨幣]]></category><category><![CDATA[比特幣]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1077559</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>世界流行加密貨幣，比特幣、以太幣，以至最近興起的狗狗幣，均為中國政府所禁，並列為非法金融行動，下令禁止人民私下 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>世界流行加密貨幣，比特幣、以太幣，以至最近興起的狗狗幣，均為中國政府所禁，並列為非法金融行動，下令禁止人民私下加密挖礦。富貴險中求，有中國礦工願承擔違法後果，偷偷開採比特幣。</p><p>中國政府認為，加密貨幣可能影響國家經濟，而開採過程亦耗費大量能源，不利持續發展。因些，中國政加強了整治工作，例如要求地方官員進行檢查、篩選非法採礦活動的 IP 地址、突襲非法地下加密礦場等等。據外媒報道，全球有超過 2 成比特幣礦工仍在中國。一些地下組織依然活躍在中國各地，如廣東、江蘇、浙江和山東省等，每天平均有 109,000 個活躍 IP。</p><p>報道續指，中國非法挖礦的幾名礦工，把其挖礦的設備送到哈薩克、美國或其他電價較低國家；較大型的礦場就則將所有設備留在國內。當中，小型礦場可透過將礦場分散成更小的單位，或使用當地未連接到電網的能源發電機組等方法，躲過審查。</p><p>在中國打擊國內礦場後，不少礦工開始往外移，目標是電價稅收相宜，又有充足再生能源的地方，因此北歐地區就成為了眾人的目標之一。瑞典的金管會會長 Erik Thedéen 和環保局局長 Björn Risinger 表示，加密貨幣的開採過程，將增加能源的消耗，他們亦因此寫封信呼籲歐盟限制挖礦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1077566 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/7bba14de-3219-4ce4-b649-8a50af2c07c5-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/7bba14de-3219-4ce4-b649-8a50af2c07c5-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/7bba14de-3219-4ce4-b649-8a50af2c07c5-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/7bba14de-3219-4ce4-b649-8a50af2c07c5.jpeg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲環保局局長 Björn Risinger（左），瑞典的金管會會長 Erik Thedéen （右）</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2021/12/18/chinas-underground-bitcoin-miners-.html">CNBC</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><div id="entry-content-1077387" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p>unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></p></div></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=mrD31kTLtNU:_-JZDZPnVIk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=mrD31kTLtNU:_-JZDZPnVIk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>成人女優利用元宇宙攪 Party   元宇宙 JAV 樂園將於 Sandbox 成立</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/javpark/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=javpark</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 06:39:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078256</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日本性感女優橋本有菜（橋本ありな）宣佈將會於元宇宙 The Sandbox 搞派對，成為第一個在元宇宙搞派對的 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日本性感女優橋本有菜（橋本ありな）宣佈將會於元宇宙 The Sandbox 搞派對，成為第一個在元宇宙搞派對的性感女優。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">Merry Christmas🎄<br />仮想空間メタバースでパーティを開く初めての女優になることができてとてもうれしいです！<br />So excited to be the 1st actress to host a party in Metaverse!</p><p>Arina Day 2022 <a href="https://twitter.com/avycnft?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@avycnft</a><br />遊びに来てね💕<br />事前登録受付中:<a href="https://t.co/yNAQyTA9sS">https://t.co/yNAQyTA9sS</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Metaverse?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Metaverse</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#NFT</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/TheSandboxGame?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@TheSandboxGame</a> <a href="https://t.co/oxsaj2rm3h">pic.twitter.com/oxsaj2rm3h</a></p><p>&mdash; 橋本ありな (@Arinahashimoto1) <a href="https://twitter.com/Arinahashimoto1/status/1474255280024473609?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 24, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在昨日聖誕除夕（24 日）橋本有菜於個人 Twitter 宣佈將會在元宇宙空間 The Sandbox 搞派對。The Sandbox 將會建立「AV Wonderland」召集成人電影愛好者。在派對開始之前她已透露了個人在 The Sandbox 的肖像。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078258" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59-768x514.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.59.jpg 834w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在背後搞派對的 AVYC，已在 The Sandbox 購入了 2 塊 3&#215;3 的土地，將會興建 JAV 主題樂園，當中會有魔法鏡子車以及成人影片中經常出現的著名情節。AVYC 現在已成為一個有 10000 NFT 的集合，收集了各種區塊鏈上的收藏品，而主題樂園將可使用專用貨幣 $AVGL 入場與交易 。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-1280x877.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-768x526.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-1536x1052.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-2048x1403.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-25-下午 2.35.55-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/Arinahashimoto1/status/1474255280024473609">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://avyc.io/?code=TkSrJJJ">AVYC</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Yr9KyM1lU68:CCOhICim3qk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Yr9KyM1lU68:CCOhICim3qk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本教授發明「可舔式」有味道電視，烹飪節目食物可供觀眾「品嚐」</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/25/tastetv/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tastetv</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 25 Dec 2021 04:16:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1078147</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日本明治大學教授宮下芳明開發出一款「可舔式」電視，在視覺以外為用戶提供味覺體驗。 &#160; 這款電視叫品嚐 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>日本明治大學教授宮下芳明開發出一款「可舔式」電視，在視覺以外為用戶提供味覺體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-694x424.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="424" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-694x424.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25-768x469.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg 1201w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-694x369.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="369" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-694x369.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51-768x409.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.51.jpg 1261w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-694x297.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="297" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-694x297.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29-768x329.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg 1279w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這款電視叫品嚐電視「Taste the TV」，簡稱為「TTTV」。電視裡面內置一個薄膜以及含有不同味道的液體，電視會根據要求，從 10 款甜酸苦辣為基礙味道的液體中，選出合適的味道並按比例噴灑到畫面上，模擬出食物味道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg" alt="" width="510" height="553" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41-768x417.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.41.jpg 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33-768x416.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.33.jpg 1181w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>當電視在熒幕顯示食物時，用戶可用舌頭舔嚐到味道，同時滿足視覺與聽覺體驗。教授指目前電視可模擬出 20 款不同食物的味道。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-694x448.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="448" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-694x448.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50-768x496.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg 1210w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.00.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1078151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18-768x439.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.18.jpg 1193w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.29.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.20.50.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-24-14.19.25.jpg"><br /></a></p><p>宮下芳明教授指電視可用作調酒師、廚師的教學影片，也可用來品嚐食物或玩猜謎遊戲。他更希望可開發一個像音樂串流平台的系統，讓用家可「下載」世界各地不同味道。</p><p>商用版 TTTV 的成本為每部 10 萬日元（約港幣 7000 元）。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_25691"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rt0CsOAls-s?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：YouTube</p></p><div class="feedflare">
